request.description:
WebSocket connection for real-time order status updates. Auto-subscribes to the specified order.

Example messages received:

1. Connection confirmation:
{
  "type": "connected",
  "clientId": "client-abc123",
  "subscribedTo": "65abc123def456789"
}

2. Status updates:
{
  "type": "status_update",
  "orderId": "65abc123def456789",
  "status": "ROUTING",
  "timestamp": "2025-01-20T10:30:01.000Z",
  "metadata": {
    "message": "Fetching quotes from DEXs"
  }
}

3. Error:
{
  "type": "error",
  "message": "Order not found"
}

WebSocket connection for general order stream. Subscribe to specific orders by sending:

{
  "action": "subscribe",
  "orderId": "65abc123def456789"
}

Unsubscribe:
{
  "action": "unsubscribe",
  "orderId": "65abc123def456789"
}
